{"title":"信念","authors":["宋树根"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":5,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋树根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是所有的草木都会开花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是所有的花朵都会结果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是所有的幼苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能长成参天大树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是所有的大树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能成为雕龙栋梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一颗石子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就去铺路吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必非得雄踞于大厦之顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一支蜡烛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就去燃烧吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕只能照亮茅屋的一角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城铸就了我的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河融进了我的血脉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取泰山为骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化黑土为肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一座高峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一拱长桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷打不惊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨浇不灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹不散"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该流血时决不淌汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是一个普通士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对您的承诺"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}